data.title: Atlanta Greek Picnic : Celebrating 20 years of D9 Unity and Culture.
data.meta_description: Join us at the 2024 Atlanta Greek Picnic June 25-30th to celebrate 20 years of Greek unity and culture! Experience the best of Divine Nine traditions, including step shows, yard shows, and more in a vibrant display of multicultural fellowship. Be part of this empowering and inclusive event in Atlanta.
data.text:
Browse our events by day and select which events you and your group would like to attend.

If attending more than one day, consider our VIP packages for maximum savings.
